buffalo - buffalo buffalo buffalo buffalo buffalo buffalo
=========================================================
buffalo is a simple, modeless, ncurses-less text editor

Requirements
------------
buffalo requires a POSIX compliant c std lib.
buffalo is otherwise self contained, it should have come with a codes.h and codes.c
which is what it uses to talk to the terminal.

Installing
----------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (need to set install and man paths)
You may also want to create a config.h, config.def.h is the default.

Afterwards you should be able to install buffalo with (root may be required):

    make clean install


Running buffalo
---------------

    buffalo


